import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { FormControl, FormGroup, Validators } from '@angular/forms'; @Component({ selector: 'app-add-albums', templateUrl: './add-albums.component.html', styleUrls: ['./add-albums.component.css'] }) export class AddAlbumsComponent { updateFiles($event: any) { console.log($event.target.files) } add() { console.log(this.album.value) } album!: FormGroup; ngOnInit(): void { this.album = new FormGroup({ title: new FormControl('', [ Validators.required, Validators.pattern('[0-9 a-z A-Z]+'), ]), creationDate: new FormControl(new Date(), [ Validators.required, ]), archived: new FormControl(0), coverPicture: new FormControl('', [Validators.minLength(5)]), photos: new FormControl([]), }); } }
